Product description

Wireless Remotely Control

You can control smart outdoor plug anywhere via Smart Life APP, it can be applied to 2HP pool pumps

Outdoor Wifi Outlet

The rubber socket covers help prevent rain from getting in, wet, snow, and cold conditions

TESSAN Outdoor Smart Wi-Fi Plug with 3 Individual Socket

The two outlets can be controlled independently or simultaneously, you can name each socket by smart devices, which control each switch clearly. It is an ideal outdoor light switch applied to outdoor lights, decorations string lights, landscape lights, patio lights, garden lights, fountains, pond pumps, lawn mowers, pool pumps, sprinkler system, etc

Hands -free Voice Control

The smart outlet compatiable with Alexa and Google assistant; Simply make a voice command to remotely turn on/off the connected devices, which makes your life easier

How to Connect TESSAN Wi-Fi Smart Outlet?

Notice: Scan the QR code of instruction to download and install the Smart Life app for iOS 8.0 Higher or Android phone 4.4 higher. Make sure your Wi-Fi network is 2.4G.

Specification

Material: Plastic
Waterproof Level: IP44
Parameters: AC 100-240V 50/60Hz
Max Power: 1875W (Resistance loading)
Max Current: 15A
Rated Voltage: 125V
Working Temperature: -20~60℃(-4~140℉)
Notice: Support 2.4Ghz Wifi only, dual-band (2.4G&5G) WIFI need to set a separate 2.4G channel.

  • How to set the smart outdoor plug?

    In the smart life app, there is a smart module about programming. You can choose and edit smart programs in the App. Here as an example for sunrise and sunset, you can refer to the attachment for operation.

  • How to connect the outdoor timer?

    1. press the power button for 5-10s to check if the indicator blinks quickly

    2. Add this device to the Smart Life app

    3. Select "Electrician" -> "Socket(Wi-Fi)" -> enter 2.4G wifi password

    4. Go back to the app to connect and complete the pairing

  • Why outdoor wifi outlet can't connect to the wifi?

    1. Please check the number of devices connected to wifi router, When the number of devices exceeds the performance of the router, the wifi connection would be unstable or failed.

    2. Your phone must connect to the 2.4G wifi when pairing

  • Can the outdoor smart plug be waterproof？

    Yes, TESSAN outdoor smart plug with IP44 is waterproof, the rubber socket covers to help prevent rain from getting in, and withstands damp, wet, snow, and cold conditions.

    Wow, when combined with Alexa, this is AI (not at all in its infancy). I set it up to control a waterfall fountain (they make them for use in back yards, in bedrooms, etc.). Yeah, you can use your phone to turn it on and off. BUT you need a lot of patience or some good tech support because there are three apps to deal with using instructions that look well organized but are not always clear and may be difficult for some (like me) to follow. Took me a day and a half and some great tech support, but it got done and it is amazing ! Works exactly as advertised.

    I purchased this to run my pool pump which is a 15amp circuit. I used this on a 12/3 extension cord and it will overheat. I installed this on the plug end as well as in the power supplying plug and still had overheating issues with it turning off. I wasn’t aware of this... See more
    I purchased this to run my pool pump which is a 15amp circuit. I used this on a 12/3 extension cord and it will overheat. I installed this on the plug end as well as in the power supplying plug and still had overheating issues with it turning off. I wasn’t aware of this until I was home at the time it came on and it was turning off and on outside the programmed setting. The app that you program it with is somewhat misleading. I programmed it to turn on between 1200pm and 3pm figuring that is what it would do. You have to create 2 separate tasks to actually make that happen. 1 to turn it on and 1 to turn it off. Once I figured that out I was good. The timer runs off of mtn time and I was unable to adjust that in the app so I had to just calculate that into my programming. Since it continued to shut down, it serves no use to me for the intended reason I purchased it and it became a waste of money. Now if you have a pool pump that runs off way less amperage than it is rated for it may be a great item.
